TopicTitle: Chinese Chang'e 5 precursor transported to launch center/ given name

Articles.Content:
It has been recently confirmed that the Chang'e 5 test mission, now designated Chang'e 5-T1, has been transported by plane and trucks to Xichang launch center for launch later this year.

Rumours have been circling that it will launch on the 24th October and will orbit the moon, not just flyby.
